<div id="page-faq" class="page">
  <div class="page-header" data-text="FAQ">
    <div class="section-label">Help</div>
    <h1>FREQUENTLY ASKED<br><em>QUESTIONS</em></h1>
    <p>Everything you need to know about training at Brisbane Boxing.</p>
  </div>
  <section style="background:var(--dark)">
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>Do I need to book before I come?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">As our classes will only have limited spaces available, ALL of our memberships (including passes) are required to book before coming in. Classes are available through booking only via our website and our own Brisbane Boxing mobile app.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>What equipment do I need?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">We require all class participants to have their own wraps, gloves, and towel as a minimum requirement. If you do not have your own wraps or gloves, they are available for purchase at each of our West End and Mt Gravatt gyms. We also stock a wide range of UBOX gear.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>How fit do I need to be?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Our classes are designed to cater for all skill and fitness levels, so we encourage everyone to try to the best of their ability, regardless of fitness or experience.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>I have never boxed before &mdash; is that okay?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">We welcome all people, it doesn't matter if you have never boxed a day in your life. We will help you with technique and you will develop skills as you train.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>What should I wear?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">We recommend you wear comfortable active wear and enclosed sneakers. Please bring a towel, and make sure you bring your hand wraps and gloves &mdash; these are available for purchase at all gym locations if you don't already have them.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>Are children allowed?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Yes &mdash; children from 12 can train at any of our classes. We require a parent or guardian to sign a waiver form prior to attending for any children under 18. Children from aged 10 can attend while accompanied by a parent or guardian. All participants including children must have hand wraps. We also offer dedicated Pee Wees classes for ages 6&ndash;12.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>Do you have shower facilities?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Our Mt Gravatt and West End gyms have mens and womens showers available to members.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>Can I train by myself when classes are on?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Class participants have priority on all equipment during class times, so the use of equipment is subject to approval by the trainer.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>How often would I need to train?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">It all depends on you! We have members that train most days with us and others that only attend a few sessions per month. It comes down to time, goals, and how your body feels.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>Do I have to spar?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Sparring isn't a requirement as part of training. Any sparring will need to be approved by coaches.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>Are ladies welcome?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Absolutely! We pride ourselves on being welcoming to all people. The majority of our Cardio Box classes are women, and we have a number of female boxing trainers on our Brisbane Boxing team. We also offer a dedicated Women's Strength Box class.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span>Do you provide refunds?</span><span class="icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">We do not refund any membership or pass payments unless they were erroneous or otherwise noted. There are no refunds or exchanges on any worn merchandise, gloves, or anything that has been worn. We also do not refund 3, 6, and 12 month memberships if not used.</div></div>
    </div>
